@startuml shawntabrizi_Ethereum-Twitter-Bounty

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor<<Smart Contract>> LightGreen
  BackgroundColor<<Frontend>> LightBlue
  BackgroundColor<<External>> LightYellow
}

[TwitterBounty.sol] <<Smart Contract>>
[TwitterOracle.sol] <<Smart Contract>>
[Truffle Framework] as Truffle
[Web3.js] as Web3
[TruffleContract] as TruffleContract
[Frontend (HTML/CSS/JS)] as Frontend <<Frontend>>
[Provable Things Oracle] as Oracle <<External>>
[Twitter API] as TwitterAPI <<External>>

database "Ethereum Blockchain" as Blockchain

TwitterBounty.sol --> TwitterOracle.sol : uses
TwitterOracle.sol --> Oracle : fetches data
Oracle --> TwitterAPI : retrieves tweets

Truffle --> TwitterBounty.sol : deploys
Truffle --> TwitterOracle.sol : deploys

Frontend --> Web3 : uses
Frontend --> TruffleContract : uses
Web3 --> Blockchain : interacts
TruffleContract --> Blockchain : interacts

TwitterBounty.sol --> Blockchain : stores state
TwitterOracle.sol --> Blockchain : stores tweet data

@enduml